               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Introduction
 - The “Synopsis of Classes” (fols. 2ra-2va)
 -
                     Letter of Eusebius to Carpianus (fols. 2va-3rb)
 - Canon tables (fols.
                     4ra-7rb)
 II) Gospel of Matthew (fols. 7va-68ra)
 - List of the
                     “tituli” for the Gospel of Matthew: 68 titles (fols. 7va-8va)
 - Bǝsrāta
                     Mātewos “Gospel of Matthew” (fols. 11ra-68ra) 
 III) Gospel of Mark (fols.
                     68rb-106ra)
 - List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Mark: 51 titles
                     (fols. 68rb-68vb)
 - Bǝsrāta Mārqos “Gospel of Mark” (fols.
                     70ra-106ra)
 IV ) Gospel of Luke (fols. 106ra-170ra)
 - List of
                     “tituli” for the Gospel of Luke: 84 titles (fols. 106ra-107va)
 - Bǝsrāta
                     Luqās “Gospel of Luke” (fols.108ra-170ra)
 V) Gospel of John
                     (fols.170rb-218rb)
 - List of “tituli” for the Gospel of John: 19 titles
                     (fol. 170rb)
 - Bǝsrāta Yoḥannǝs “Gospel of John” (fols. 171ra-218rb)
                     
 Additiones 1-6.</summary>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="2ra" to="218rb"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1560Gospel">Four Gospels</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     
                     <note>The Golden Gospel of <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0030AP">ʿĀddaqāḥarsi Ṗarāqliṭos</placeName>.</note>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1">
                        
                        <locus from="2ra" to="7v">2ra-7v</locus>
                        <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2705Introd">Introduction to the Gospels</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           ግጻዌ፡ ሠርዓት፡ በእንተ፡ ፬ቃላት፡ እንዘ፡ ይተሉ፡
                           ረድኤተ፡ ክልኤቱ፡ ባሕቲቶሙ፡ ጸሐፉ፡ እንከ፡ ወንጌል፡ እምሐዋርያት፡ ክልኤቱ...
                        </incipit>
                        
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.1">
                           <locus from="2ra" to="2va">2ra-2va</locus>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1548Gessaw">Synopsis of Classes</title>
                           <note/>
                        </msItem>                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.2">
                           <locus from="2va" to="3rb">2va-3rb</locus>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1349EpistlEusebius">Epistle of Eusebius to Carpianus (General record)</title>
                           <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1.3">
                           <locus from="4r" to="7r">4r-7r</locus>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1224Canons">Canon tables</title>
                           <note/>
                        </msItem>
                        
                        
                     </msItem>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2">
                        <locus from="7va" to="68ra">7va-68ra</locus>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1558Matthew">Wangel za-Mātewos</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>                        
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           መጽሐፈ፡ ልደቱ፡ ለኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወልደ፡ ዳዊት፡
                           ወልደ፡ አብርሃም…<foreign xml:lang="en">Book of the birth of Jesus
                              Christ, son of David, son of Abraham... </foreign>
                        </incipit>
                        <explicit>
                           <locus target="#68ra">68ra, l.2</locus> ወመህርዎሙ፡ ከመ፡ ይዕቀቡ፡ ዘአዘዝኩክሙ፡ ወናሁ፡
                           ምስሌክሙ፡ በኵሉ፡ መዋዕል፡ እስከ፡ ኅልቀተ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን፡ አሜን፨
                        </explicit>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.1">
                           <locus from="7va" to="8va">7va-8va</locus>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1558Matthew#TituliMatthew">List of the “Tituli” for the
                              Gospel of Matthew – 58 titles</title>
                           <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2.2">
                           <locus from="11ra" to="68ra">11ra-68ra</locus>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2709Matthew">Bǝsrāta Mātewos</title>
                           <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                           <note>The traditional opening lines to the Gospel are missing.</note>
                        </msItem>
                        
                     </msItem>
                     
                     
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                        <locus from="68rb" to="106ra">68rb-106ra</locus>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1882MarkGo">Wangel za-Mārqos</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                            ቀዳሚሁ፡ ለወንጌል፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወልደ፡
                           እግዚአብሔር…<foreign xml:lang="en">

                              Beginning of the Gospel of Jesus
                              Christ, son of God...</foreign>
                        </incipit>
                        <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                           <locus target="#105vb">105vb, l. 19</locus> ወወፂኦሙ፡ እሙንቱ፡ ሰባኩ፡ ኵልሂ፡ እንዘ፡ እግዚ
                           [<pb/>] አብሔር፡ ይረድእ፡ ወቃሎ፡ ያጸንዕ፡ በተአምር፡
                           ዘይተሉ፡ አሜን፨
                        </explicit>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.1">
                           <locus from="68rb" to="68vb">68rb-68vb</locus>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1882MarkGo#TituliMark"> of “Tituli” for the
                              Gospel of Mark – 51 titles</title>
                           <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                           
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.2">
                           <locus from="70ra" to="106ra"/>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2711Mark">Bǝsrāta Mārqos</title>
                           <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                           <note>The traditional opening lines to the Gospel are missing.</note>
                        </msItem>
                        
                     </msItem>
                     
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                        <locus from="106ra" to="170ra">106ra-170ra</locus>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1812GospelLuke">Wangel za-Luqās</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           <locus target="#108ra">108ra</locus> እስመ፡ ብዙኃን፡ እለ፡ አኀዙ፡ ወጠኑ፡ ይንግሩ፡
                           ወይምሀሩ፡ በእንተ፡ ግብር፡ ዘአምኑ፡ በላዕሌነ…<foreign xml:lang="en">
                              Because many started to tell
                              and instruct about things that occurred among us…</foreign>
                        </incipit>
                        <explicit>
                           <locus target="#170ra">170ra</locus>ወተሰውጡ፡ ኢየሩሳሌም፡ በዐቢይ፡ ፍሥሐ፡ ወነበሩ፡
                           ቤተ፡ መቅደስ፡ ዘልፈ፡ እንዘ፡ ይባርክዎ፡ ወይሴብሕዎ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ለዓለም፡ አሜን፨
                        </explicit>
                        
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.1">
                           <locus from="106ra" to="107va"/>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1812GospelLuke#TituliLuke">List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of Luke –
                              84 titles</title>
                           <textLang mainLang="gez"/>                           
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4.2">
                           <locus from="108ra" to="170ra"/>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2713Luke">Bǝsrāta Luqās</title>
                           <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                           <note>The traditional opening lines to the Gospel are
                              missing</note>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>
                     
                     <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                        <locus from="170rb" to="218rb">170rb-218rb</locus>
                        <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1693John">Gospel of John</title>
                        <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                           <locus target="#171ra">171ra</locus>ቀዳሚሁ፡ ቃል፡ ውእቱ፡ ወውእቱ፡ ቃል፡ ኀበ፡
                           እግዚአብሔር፡ ውእቱ፡ ወእግዚአብሔር፡ ውእቱ፡ ቃል...<foreign xml:lang="en">
                              In the beginning was the Word,
                              and the Word was with God, and the word was God...</foreign>
                        </incipit>
                        <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                           <locus target="#218rb">218rb</locus>ወሶበ፡ ተጽሕፈ፡ ኵሉ፡ በበ፡ አሐዱ፡ እመ፡
                           ኢያግመሮ፡ ዓለም፡ ጥቀ፡ መጸሕፍቲሁ፡ ዘእምተጽሕፈ፡ አሜን፨
                        </explicit>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5.1">
                           <locus target="#170rb">170rb</locus>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1693John#TituliJohn">List of the “tituli” for the Gospel of John – 19 titles</title>
                           <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                           
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5.2">
                           <locus from="171ra" to="218rb"/>
                           <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2715John">Gospel of John</title>
                           <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                           <note>The traditional opening lines to the Gospel are missing.</note>
                        </msItem>
                     </msItem>
